          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-947B907A-line-1" n="1">You always are making a God of your Spouse;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-947B907A-line-2" n="2">But this neither Reason nor Conscience allows.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-947B907A-line-3" n="3">Perhaps you will say── 'tis in Gratitude due,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-947B907A-line-4" n="4">And that you adore <hi rend="italics">him</hi>, because he adores <hi rend="italics">you</hi>.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-947B907A-line-5" n="5">Your Argument's weak; &amp; so you will find;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-947B907A-line-6" n="6">For you, by <hi rend="italics">this</hi> Rule, must adore <hi rend="italics">all Mankind</hi>.</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
      </div>
